name: Through The Window Tribute
description:
Through the window was my very first project as a street photographer. I was afraid to take images head on, so in order to build confidence I took all my photographs through the window. When I first started shooting I wasn't to fond of this practice, but looking back at these images always re-sparks my interest in these type of photos.

My tribute to @jjjjjohn Window Still Life #OBJKT4OBJK
